safe country
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:winter country, i.e. land where sheep can graze for the winter without becoming snow-bound.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:winter country
